Check center angle of points to input order

Source: R/plot.R
Lrad.plot.Rd

Check center angle of points to input order

Usage

Lrad.plot(L, i.ring = 1:9)

Arguments

L

list of tree rings

i.ring

integer vector, tree ring number for drawing

Examples

slotNames(TR)
#>  [1] "P_filename"  "P_id.tag"    "P_ring.tag"  "P"           "P00"        
#>  [6] "n_id"        "YR_P"        "L_filename"  "L_ring.tag"  "L"          
#> [11] "L_"          "YR_L"        "ln"          "L2_filename" "L2"         
#> [16] "n_YR"       
Lplot(TR@L)
